description: Telegram says it will now provide user data to the police; the walls are closing in on the Snowflake hacker; and why Nintendo's lawsuit against Palworld is bad (and Nintendo will probably win).
title: Podcast: Telegram is Working With the Cops

description: Orpheus Network tells users: "With great displeasure we need to inform you that a malicious actor has successfully carried out a massive peer scraping attack on our tracker."
title: Major Private Music Torrenting Site Suffers ‘Massive Peer Scraping Attack’
